Feature: MainTreadsOfApp

  As a user
  I want to see green icon in Windows Tray
  To know that application is run

  Scenario: Add green icon to Windows Tray
    Given application is not run
    When I run application
    Then in Windows Tray add green icon

  As a user
  I want to have 4 items in application menu

  Scenario: menu of icon in Windows Tray
    Given application is not run
    When I run application
    Then my application have popup menu of 4 items